data.description: Save thousands of dollars a month with this 2.25% assumable VA 30-year mortgage loan in this truly one-of-a-kind SMART HOME nestled on over half an acre lot in the charming Annsbrooke Community. Step inside, and you're greeted by a majestic 2-story foyer, with an abundance of natural light, and soaring vaulted ceilings. This home is packed with advanced features, from Brilliant Home control panels to Ring security systems and so much more. Discover the comfort and style of two inviting fireplaces, spacious living areas, and a chef-ready kitchen equipped with smart stainless-steel appliances. The main floor is home to a master suite with a walk-in closet and a lavish ensuite bathroom. Upstairs, you'll find three bedrooms and two bathrooms, while the fully finished daylight basement, complete with a private entrance, offers the ideal space for an in-law suite. Step outside to an immaculate backyard, complemented by a freshly painted wooden deck and a delightful vegetable garden, all seamlessly integrated with smart home features. Here, low-maintenance living reaches its pinnacle within the sought-after Swim/Tennis Community, just minutes from I-75 and McDonough Highway, as well as an array of shopping and dining options.
